{"tid":1780710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要記住我哋只係未贏，唔係已經輸","createTime":"2019-12-12T15:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T16:04:35.000Z","uid":31004,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb07ba3252e52b6e245f4e307a9068ef75bb4493","tid":1780710,"uid":31004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"依排好多失敗post，無可否認運動去到樽頸位，大家都唔知仲有咩可以做，好迷惘<br />\n<br />\n好老實講，我都唔知可以點，但係我希望大家要記得，我哋未輸㗎<br />\n<br />\n我哋真正輸嗰日，係無人再提五大訴求，當哂義士係condom嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n80萬人上街遊行好少？03年23條立法加沙士都係50萬人，香港2019年之前咁耐都係得一次百萬人大遊行，就係六四<br />\n<br />\n唔係一定要十八區開花先叫有嘢做緊，仲有黃色經濟圈，連儂牆，我哋要做嘅係唔好習慣，唔好忘記<br />\n<br />\n煲底見從來都唔係講笑，我係深信有依一日<br />\n<br />\n只要我哋唔好好似以前咁，年年淨係去六四晚會七一遊行當買贖罪券，每人行多步做多啲，我哋總有一日會贏<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47d660615c97a541bbe03ca129fd15def257d33","tid":1780710,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國不停追擊中共</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">tweets響哂task2</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=cb789abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: red;\">/task2</span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"5dfa59d5b2c7ac9d5430e1aa70da4b0225c4d214","tid":1780710,"uid":31004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor